{
  "stem": "16.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, this, this brother-in-law of, of my cousin, he was with me all the time in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like I said, his number was 4343.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were working in a-- in a factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it belonged to Krupp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They came-- what this factory had is boxcars, bombed-out boxcars, the iron twisted, the-- like the type of box cars that we were dragged in to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It, it had all kinds of damages from bombs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was our job to straighten out what, what needed to be straightened out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the door, it was written in German-- in Hochdeutsch, in German-- what needs to be done to this wagon, to this boxcar, what needs to be done to that box car, and so on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And pretty soon, [SIGHS] one Polish civilian that came in every morning from his home to work-- he worked for pay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Six prisoners were assigned to this Polish prisoner-- to this Polish civilian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Down at the next boxcar, another Polish private person, six other prisoners, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was assigning you every morning as we-- as we came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You, you do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You, you do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one time, I was assigned to straighten out a-- an-- a piece of iron that was yea wide and long, I mean, very long.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was twisted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one guy had-- there was a-- there was a girl, a-- how do you call that when you-- when you cut iron in half with fire?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A welder.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sawing it off?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A welder, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a girl that had those big gloves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was the welder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was heating up that piece of iron.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On one side, one guy had to stand there and hold something stiff, very strong.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
